<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Equipe <%= numero %></title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f9ff; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,119,182,0.1); }
    h1 { color: #0077b6; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p { color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Equipe <%= numero %></h1>
    <p>Em desenvolvimento...</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
